I'm writing to report a critical issue that is currently blocking all Kalshi trading activities. The Kalshi API endpoints (`api.kalshi.com` and `trade-api.kalshi.com`) are not resolving through DNS. I've confirmed this using multiple DNS servers, including Google's public DNS, and they consistently return `NXDOMAIN` (Non-Existent Domain).

